sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer as "Customer"
    participant System as "Customer Prediction System"
    participant Model as "Prediction Model"
    participant Database as "Database"

    Customer->>>System: Provides customer data
    System->>>Database: Retrieves historical customer data
    Database->>>System: Returns historical customer data
    System->>>Model: Inputs data into prediction model
    Model->>>System: Generates prediction
    System->>>Customer: Outputs prediction result